Title: As an app user I can top up my account balance
as a user I can see a list of my accounts
As an app user I can view my account balance
as a user I can create an account
As an app user I can draw down my funds
As an app user I can transfer money to another account
DB Schema migrations should be possible
As an app user I should be able to top up my account balance and send the money to another user in the same transaction
As an app user I can view my transaction history
As an app user I should not be able to put my account into negative balance
As an app user I can send money in currencies other than my own
As an app user I want my account to be accessible only by me
